title: Sawbones: Stroke
description:
Today, we're honoring the memory of Luke Perry who passed away this week after a stroke. We'll be talking about the history of strokes, but more importantly teach you how to help prevent them and how to spot them when they happen.

Music: "Medicines" by The Taxpayers
author: sawbones@maximumfun.org (Justin McElroy)
